- Added scale controls! They are available from `Properties` option.
- Added Saved Presets - players can now save / restore their own private presets! They are limited in amount by config.
- Setting name of Armor Stand to empty fully hides it, instead of leaving empty nameplate.
- When selecting presets, "Paste Settings with Inventory" option will no longer be shown.
- Fixed some uis not playing the click sound.
- Fixed some texts using 0/1 instead of true/false
- Marker Armor Stands are no longer highlighted with particles.
- More internal preparation for removal of legacy ui.